name: Super Stickman Run: Go to Rescue Princess
name_original: Super Stickman Run: Go to Rescue Princess
description:
Super Stickman Run will lead you step back in time to your childhood with the legendary mission: Princess Rescue.
How to Play:
* Control buttons to run, jump blocks and explore the arcades.
* Travel across dangerous jungle, desert, machinery base, etc.
* Collect coins, gold, acceleration props to help you defeat the Monster!

FEATURE:
- Exciting campaign: complete challenging missions in 8 worlds, each world has 4 levels
- Horrible thing note: Huge boss, challenge him and Save the Princess.
- Classic platform game style.
- Game is free, no purchase required.
- Suitable with kids and children.

Download Super Stickman Run and play it now to help you remember your own intense childhood.
